ing Cappadocia from above is sensational, however, maybe even better is experiencing the balloons from the ground too! Get up early, and walk to a viewpoint, to watch the glow of the balloons against the pinks and oranges of the morning sky.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-49932 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104419\/cappadocia-turkey-best-viewpoint-hot-air-balloon-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\