take-off, it&#x2019;s best to rent a bike or motorbike the evening before. When you wake up, search on Google Maps for &#x2018;The Dalton Brothers&#x2019;, and you&#x2019;ll find a road that runs at the foot of the valley. Follow this for about 5 minutes and park as soon as you see hot air balloons beginning to light up. From here, hike up as high as you can onto one of the ridges and experience balloons flying all around you as the night stars fade, and the sun rises.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/cappadocia-balloon-flight\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a Balloon Flight easily online.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-1080x808.jpg\" alt=\"cappadocia things to do hot air balloons\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cappadocia things to do hot air balloons\" class=\"wp-image-49935 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-1080x808.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-600x449.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-1536x1150.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-241x180.jpg 241w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-768x575.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-1024x766.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-1440x1078.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-30x22.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104415\/cappadocia-things-to-do-hot-air-balloons-1080x808.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Another option is to head to Lovers Hill, another panoramic viewpoint in Goreme town. It&#x2019;s a great place at sunrise to watch the balloons take off, or a peaceful place to simply sit and watch the sun go down.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Also, see the full <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/turkey\/turkey-route-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Turkey Route trip (opens in a new tab)\">Turkey Route trip<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2><strong>4. Pasabag and Cappadocia Open Air Museum<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pasabag, also known as &#x2018;Valley of the Monks&#x2019;, is where the mushroom-shaped rock formations live. With large rocks that seem to balance on top of them, these chimneys are dotted all over the valley and were once an important settlement for monks. As a result, many of them were carved into churches, and now over 30 rock churches are open for visitors. Make sure you take the opportunity to visit inside and even climb to the top!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag.jpg\" alt=\"cappadocia best things to do Pasabag\"><\/noscript><img width=\"249\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cappadocia best things to do Pasabag\" class=\"wp-image-49911 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1417px) 100vw, 1417px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag.jpg 1417w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-300x406.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-600x813.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-443x600.jpg 443w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-598x810.jpg 598w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-249x338.jpg 249w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-1134x1536.jpg 1134w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-120x163.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-133x180.jpg 133w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-567x768.jpg 567w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-756x1024.jpg 756w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-797x1080.jpg 797w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-1063x1440.jpg 1063w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104443\/cappadocia-best-things-to-do-Pasabag.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Be aware that Pasabag can become very busy as it is a popular stop-off on many organized tour circuits. If you want to see it when it&#x2019;s quiet and snap some photos without people in them, we advise visiting at sunrise. The area is free to enter!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-photography-tips\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">14 travel photography tips to improve your Instagram<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-