rhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel-720x1080.jpg 720w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel-960x1440.jpg 960w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel.jpg 1280w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104435\/cappadocia-turkey-travel-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3><strong>Cappadocia Open Air Museum<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another must-see is the Cappadocia Open Air Museum, one of Turkey&#x2019;s <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO World Heritage<\/a> sites. It is located in Goreme, only a 15-minute walk from the city center, so it&#x2019;s a fun and easy thing to visit if you&#x2019;re staying in the town. The Open Air Museum is home to many magnificent churches carved within the rock and have stunning frescoes painted on the walls.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Entrance fee: <\/strong>The Open Air Museum entrance is around 40 TL, which is around USD 3. You pay more to visit this museum than Pasabag because of the paintings, and it&#x2019;s well worth it!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/cappadocia-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find all Cappadocia hotels<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/01095353\/cappadocia-turkey-Open-Air-Museum.jpg\" alt=\"cappadocia turkey Open Air Museum\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cappadocia turkey Open Air Museum\" class=\"wp-image-54876 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/01095353\/cappadocia-turkey-Open-Air-Museum.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/01095353\/cappadocia-turkey-Open-Air-Museum-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/01095353\/cappadocia-turkey-Open-Air-Museum-6