ck-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2><strong>5. Get Lost in a Maze of Rugs<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There&#x2019;s a famous carpet shop in Goreme, named &#x2018;Galeri Ikman&#x2019;. This is one of the best places to get beautiful photos of colorful Turkish rugs and other kinds of traditional handicrafts. It&#x2019;s absolutely huge, with over 50,000 pieces of craftsmanship divided into 17 rooms! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456\/cappadocia-things-to-do-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"cappadocia things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cappadocia things to do\" class=\"wp-image-49900 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456\/cappadocia-things-to-do-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456\/cappadocia-things-to-do-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456\/cappadocia-things-to-do-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456\/cappadocia-things-to-do-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456\/cappadocia-things-to-do-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456\/cappadocia-things-to-do-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456\/cappadocia-things-to-do-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456\/cappadocia-things-to-do-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104456