block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"besttime\"><strong>Best Time to Visit Cappadocia<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cappadocia is beautiful in all seasons; however, try to avoid July and August because of the heat, crowds of tourists, and higher prices. Late spring or early autumn is the ideal time for a peaceful visit, with mild temperatures and lower prices.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, you&#x2019;ll see that lots of people visit Cappadocia on a day trip, but one day is not enough to soak up the atmosphere of this stunning place. We recommend visiting for 3-4 days in order to hike, relax, take a hot air balloon ride, and do many other outdoor activities on offer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/02085417\/Hot-Air-Balloons-cappadocia-turkey.jpg\" alt=\"Hot Air Balloons cappadocia turkey\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Hot Air Balloons cappadocia turkey\" class=\"wp-image-54891 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/02085417\/Hot-Air-Balloons-cappadocia-turkey.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/02085417\/Hot-Air-Balloons-cappadocia-turkey-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/02085417\/Hot-Air-Balloons-cappadocia-turkey-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/02085417\/Hot-Air-Balloons-cappadocia-turkey-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/02085417\/Hot-Air-Balloons-cappadocia-turkey-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/02085417\/Hot-Air-Balloons-cappadocia-turkey-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/w