in<\/a> &#x2013; was our number one favorite restaurant in Cappadocia<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/sedef-goreme\/\">Sedef Restaurant<\/a> &#x2013; This is the perfect place to try the famous pottery kebab: a typical meat stew that comes inside a pot that you have to break open.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/firin-goreme\/\">Firin Express<\/a> &#x2013; serves the most delicious (and cheap) flatbreads!<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/dibek-goreme\/\">Dibek<\/a> &#x2013; serves the overall best traditional food<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-become-vegetarian\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Read:<\/strong> How to become vegetarian in 8 simple steps<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104358\/best-food-cappadocia-turkey-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"best food cappadocia turkey\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best food cappadocia turkey\" class=\"wp-image-49947 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104358\/best-food-cappadocia-turkey-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/23104358\/b